original_title: Richmond: Beach Street - Van Duzer Street
text:
70 Beach Street, south side, between Van Duzer Street and Union Place (Stapleton), showing the Liberty Theatre. The view is westward.

March 23, 1930.

P.L. Sperr.

original_title: Richmond: Van Duzer Street - Beach Street
text:
Van Duzer Street, north of, and adjoining the N. W. corner of Beach Street. Beers's 1874 map shows the two houses to have been owned by R. M. Hazard. The view is south.

February 9, 1930

P. L. Sperr

original_title: Richmond: Beach Street - Van Duzer Street
text:
129, 131, and 135-137 (right to left) Beach Street, north side, between Van Duzer and Jackson Streets (Stapleton). The view is eastward.

October 8, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.
